<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lengthen" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lengthen,</orth> to draw out, to extend, to make longer in space or time: Lucr. Dedic. <bibl n="shak. pp 210" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 210</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.2.138" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. Ind. 2, 138.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.4.16" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 4, 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.12" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 2, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.208" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 208</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.43" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.353" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 353</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.1.169" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 1, 169</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.3.13" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 3, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.4.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 4, 46</bibl>. <cit><quote>I shall short my word by --ing my return,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 1.6.201" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 6, 201</bibl></cit> (== delaying, retarding). With <emph>out</emph>: <cit><quote>to l. out the worst,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 3.2.199" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 III, 2, 199</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>